    <item>
      <title>Talktiv v0.5.0</title>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2026 18:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>3</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.5.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>Talktiv v0.5.0</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Auto-updates via Sparkle</strong> — you're seeing this because it works!</li>
          <li><strong>Refreshed icons</strong> — warm gradient waveform brand across all UI</li>
          <li><strong>Fixed large model loading</strong> and meeting language persistence</li>
          <li><strong>Multi-strategy paste</strong> — CGEvent, AppleScript, and AXUIElement fallback</li>
          <li><strong>Smart media control</strong> — checks actual playback state via MediaRemote</li>
          <li><strong>Meeting auto-detect</strong> — window title analysis, not just app launch</li>
          <li><strong>Speaker diarization</strong> — audio feature analysis for multiple speakers</li>
          <li><strong>File-based logging</strong> — diagnostics for troubleshooting</li>
          <li><strong>Issues banner</strong> — problems surface at top of Settings with one-click fixes</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
