    <item>
      <title>Talktiv v0.4.0</title>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2026 12:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>2</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.4.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>What's New in v0.4.0</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Meeting Mode</strong> — Record Zoom, Google Meet, Teams calls with live transcription and speaker identification</li>
          <li><strong>Voice Notepad</strong> — Dictate freely, edit inline, copy when done</li>
          <li><strong>Auto-detect meetings</strong> — Detects when meeting windows open, auto-starts recording</li>
          <li><strong>Speaker diarization</strong> — Identifies different speakers using audio analysis</li>
          <li><strong>Markdown export</strong> — Meetings saved as .md with YAML frontmatter</li>
          <li><strong>Meeting intelligence</strong> — Claude API for action items, decisions, summaries</li>
          <li><strong>Multi-strategy paste</strong> — CGEvent, AppleScript, and AXUIElement fallback chain</li>
          <li><strong>Smart media control</strong> — Checks actual playback state before pausing</li>
          <li><strong>File-based logging</strong> — Diagnostics at ~/Library/Application Support/Talktiv/talktiv.log</li>
          <li><strong>Auto-updates via Sparkle</strong></li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
